title: Saturday Night Live Season 25 Complete
description:
SNL Season 25 (1999-2000)

SATURDAY NIGHT LIVE RETURNS WITH IT'S 25th SEASON. BEGINNING OFF WITH THE 25th ANNIVERSARY SPECIAL ON SEPTEMBER 26th 1999. THEN THE SHOW WENT BACK ON OCTOBER 2nd 1999. SATURDAY NIGHT LIVE WENT ALIVE AND WELL. AND THIS WAS TIM MEADOWS LAST SEASON ON THE SHOW. RACHEL DRATCH WAS ALSO DEBUTED ON THE SHOW AS A FEATURED PLAYER.     AL FRANKEN ALSO RETURNED TO THE SHOW AS A SPECIAL GUEST APPEARENCE ON THE 1999 SNL CHRISTMAS SHOW. AND ALSO THE FORMER SNL CAST MEMBER:NORM McDONALD WHO GOT FIRED FROM SNL RETURN TO HOST THE SHOW.

SO HERE IS SEASON 25. The 25th ANNIVERSARY SEASON.
